 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Gerencia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:37pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Resumen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Permite modificar los datos descriptivos, categorías o parámetros de un producto existente.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Frecuencia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Media&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:24.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Precondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;El producto debe estar registrado y el usuario tener permisos de edición.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:45.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Descripción&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;El sistema carga el formulario con los datos actuales del producto. El usuario modifica los campos permitidos, tales como nombre, descripción, unidad de medida, categorías, clasificación y parámetros asociados [Excepción 1]. El sistema valida que los datos ingresados cumplan las reglas de negocio y que los campos obligatorios estén completos [Excepción 2]. Si la validación es exitosa, el sistema actualiza la información del producto en la base de datos y confirma la operación.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:61.59912109375pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepción 1: Intento de modificar el SKU. El sistema bloquea el campo e informa que el ID es inmutable.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Excepción 2: Datos inválidos o campos obligatorios vacíos. El sistema resalta el error.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Poscondiciones&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;La información del producto queda actualizada en todo el sistema.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr style=&quot;height:25.75pt&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Dependencias&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-width: 1.125pt; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: top; padding: 5pt; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;text-align: center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 9pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(234, 153, 153); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;UR 1.2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
